Media personality Minnie Dlamini-Jones has suffered another loss of a loved one. Last year, Minnie lost her brother Khosini, who spent several weeks in ICU. Now the star has revealed that she has suffered another loss of someone she loved dearly. ALSO READ; COVID-19: NASPER HAS DELIVERED FIRST SHIPMENT Taking to Twitter,  the star expressed her sadness, saying she is tired of losing people she loves. "Someone I love and have known my whole life passed away this morning. My heart is in pain. I'm tired of losing people I love," she shared with her more than 3 million Twitter followers. 